<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1249669-i-hated-the-ending-either-he-is-working">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I hated the ending. Either he is working for the dark side and luring the guy into an ambush or he is having a genuine and generous cross cultural chat. There's hints that either could be the correct ending. If you're telling a story - tell the story. Anyone agree? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1249669'><a id="like_count_community_question_1249669" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1249669?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">5 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F88815.The_Reluctant_Fundamentalist">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1249669-i-hated-the-ending-either-he-is-working">3 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1249669-i-hated-the-ending-either-he-is-working">See all 7 answers</a>
