<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1037689-who-do-you-think-the-waiter-was-or-was">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Who do you think the waiter was, or was representing, at the end? My thought was that the listening man was CIA, come to "take care of" Changez, but, if so, I wasn't sure who the waiter might be. Hope this isn't a dumb question--I'm not good at parsing out the underlying meaning of stuff! <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
