<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    The waiter is working along with Changez but it is upto Changez to whether listen to him or not. The listening is probably the guy who was send to tak<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    The waiter is working along with Changez but it is upto Changez to whether listen to him or not. The listening is probably the guy who was send to take care of Changez. Now it upto the American and Changez to decide whether to do the act their sides expect from them or not. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
