        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2283853622" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17018141766903647402">Whilst delivering one man&apos;s story, Mohsin Hamid introduces the reader to an entire nation&apos;s. This clever allegory defies traditional structure, with its unique narrative style, and transcends emotion, by seeming to produce a severe lack of it. And this frank display of truth invites the reader to query their own.<br/><br/>This is a story everyone feels they have read, in one format or another, but Hamid tears down the boundaries of this known narrative to deliver a truth everyone needs to read.</span>
  <span id="freeText17018141766903647402" style="display:none">Whilst delivering one man's story, Mohsin Hamid introduces the reader to an entire nation's. This clever allegory defies traditional structure, with its unique narrative style, and transcends emotion, by seeming to produce a severe lack of it. And this frank display of truth invites the reader to query their own.<br /><br />This is a story everyone feels they have read, in one format or another, but Hamid tears down the boundaries of this known narrative to deliver a truth everyone needs to read.</span>
